table.name: accounts_account
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE accounts_account (id integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, password varchar (128) NOT NULL, first_name varchar (50) NOT NULL, last_name varchar (50) NOT NULL, username varchar (50) NOT NULL UNIQUE, email varchar (100) UNIQUE, phone_number varchar (50) NOT NULL, date_joined datetime NOT NULL, last_login datetime NOT NULL, is_admin bool NOT NULL, is_staff bool NOT NULL, is_active bool NOT NULL, is_superuser bool NOT NULL)

table.name: auth_group
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_group" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "name" varchar(150) NOT NULL UNIQUE)

table.name: auth_group_permissions
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_group_permissions" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "group_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_group" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "permission_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "auth_permission" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: auth_permission
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "auth_permission" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "content_type_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "codename" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "name" varchar(255) NOT NULL)

table.name: carts_cart
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "carts_cart" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "cart_id" varchar(250) NOT NULL, "date_added" date NOT NULL)

table.name: carts_cartitem
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "carts_cartitem" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "quantity" integer NOT NULL, "is_active" bool NOT NULL, "product_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "store_product" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "user_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "accounts_account" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "cart_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "carts_cart" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: carts_cartitem_variations
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "carts_cartitem_variations" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "cartitem_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "carts_cartitem" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "variation_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "store_variation" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: category_category
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "category_category" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "category_name" varchar(50) NOT NULL UNIQUE, "description" text NOT NULL, "cat_image" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "slug" varchar(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE)

table.name: django_admin_log
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_admin_log" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "action_time" datetime NOT NULL, "object_id" text NULL, "object_repr" varchar(200) NOT NULL, "change_message" text NOT NULL, "content_type_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "django_content_type" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "user_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "accounts_account" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "action_flag" smallint unsigned NOT NULL CHECK ("action_flag" >= 0))

table.name: django_content_type
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_content_type" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "app_label" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "model" varchar(100) NOT NULL)

table.name: django_migrations
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_migrations" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "app" varchar(255) NOT NULL, "name" varchar(255) NOT NULL, "applied" datetime NOT NULL)

table.name: django_session
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "django_session" ("session_key" varchar(40) NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY, "session_data" text NOT NULL, "expire_date" datetime NOT NULL)

table.name: orders_order
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE orders_order (id integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, order_number varchar (50), first_name varchar (100), last_name varchar (100), phone varchar (20) NOT NULL, email varchar (254), address_line_1 varchar (255) NOT NULL, address_line_2 varchar (255), country varchar (50), state varchar (50), city varchar (50), order_note text, order_total real, tax real, status varchar (10), ip varchar (20), created_at datetime, updated_at datetime, payment_id integer REFERENCES orders_payment (id) DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, user_id integer REFERENCES accounts_account (id) DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, order_date datetime, is_ordered bool, quantity varchar (100))

table.name: orders_orderproduct
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "orders_orderproduct" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "quantity" integer NOT NULL, "product_price" real NOT NULL, "ordered" bool NOT NULL, "created_at" datetime NOT NULL, "updated_at" datetime NOT NULL, "order_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "orders_order" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "payment_id" integer NULL REFERENCES "orders_payment" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "user_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "accounts_account" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED, "color" varchar(50) NOT NULL, "size" varchar(50) NOT NULL, "product_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "store_variation" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: orders_payment
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "orders_payment" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "payment_id" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "payment_method" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "amount_paid" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "status" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "created_at" datetime NOT NULL, "user_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "accounts_account" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: store_product
table.ddl: CREATE TABLE "store_product" ("id" integer NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "product_name" varchar(200) NOT NULL UNIQUE, "slug" varchar(200) NOT NULL UNIQUE, "description" text NOT NULL, "price" integer NOT NULL, "image" varchar(100) NOT NULL, "stock" integer NOT NULL, "is_available" bool NOT NULL, "created_date" date NOT NULL, "modified_date" date NOT NULL, "category_id" integer NOT NULL REFERENCES "category_category" ("id") DEFERRABLE INITIALLY DEFERRED)

table.name: store_sitesettings
